EmailTemplate.name: Email Intro for Appt Setting Campaigns
EmailTemplate.subject: SunPower Solar for Your Home
EmailTemplate.textOnly:
Dear {!Contact.FirstName},
Thank you very much for your interest in residential solar options with SunPower and for scheduling your free/no-obligation Solar Consultation with us! We have received your information and you do appear to be a great candidate for solar savings. A SunPower Solar Advisor will be contacting you soon to confirm your information and your appointment details. Also, please be prepared to discuss your average monthly electric bill. If you are uncertain of this information, please see attached directions to obtain this from your utility provider.
Once the appointment is confirmed, you will receive an email confirmation with your appointment details as well as contact information for your SunPower Energy Consultant (who will design a custom solar electric system to meet your specific needs and answer any further questions you may have).
Thanks again for your interest in SunPower--the world's most powerful solar! For more information in the meantime, please refer to the attached brochure and feel free to visit our website: http://us.sunpower.com/homes/
Sincerely,
SunPower Customer Support www.sunpower.com
